reviews.review_text: Thanks for this great new copy It needs some EQ-warming as all SBDs do, but OMG the Terrapin melts your face off, and the rest of the show is as good!
Very very nice...omg Anything I've gotten from Charlie throughout a 30 year Span, Usually spells quality thanks for all your hard work Charlie... You sent me a few C d's on the kimock list..ja
Have A Nice Day 😊 Don’t give up! “Never know.”
